About the Author, Robert Hagstrom
Robert Hagstrom is one of the best-known authors of investment books for general audiences. He has written nine books, including the New York Times best-selling The Warren Buffett Way and The Warren Buffett Portfolio: Mastering the Power of the Focus Investment Strategy. Robert is a graduate of Villanova University with a BA and MA and is a Chartered Financial Analyst. He lives with his family in Villanova, Pennsylvania. Visit Robert's website at http://RobertHagstrom.com.
