Warren Buffett - Wikipedia




















 







Warren Buffett

From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia


					Jump to:					navigation, 					search



Warren Buffett



Warren Buffett in 2005



Born
Warren Edward Buffett
(1930-08-30) August 30, 1930 (age 86)
Omaha, Nebraska, U.S.


Residence
Omaha, Nebraska, U.S.


