 Warren Buffett


 
Actor |
 
Soundtrack





Warren Buffett was born on August 30, 1930 in Omaha, Nebraska, USA as Warren Edward Buffett. He is an actor, known for Wall Street: Money Never Sleeps (2010), Das Milliardenversprechen (2012) and The Berkshire Apprentice (2016). He has been married to Astrid Menks since August 30, 2006. He was previously married to Susan Thompson.            
See full bio »
            
 


Born:

August 30, 
     
1930

            in
            Omaha, Nebraska, USA





