Others from  The Best Businessmen in the World

 

          What do Bill Gates, Oprah Winfrey, Warren Edward Buffett have in common? They are neither well known pop stars nor actors. But they are still very influential in the world. They influence the progress and even the fashion. They are the richest and the most influential businessmen. They are highly appreciated in the world and they are highly gossiped about their financial condition. This poll offers a number of the richest businessmen in the world.          

